   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Neilos and Polion, the 2 collectors of grain-taxes of the village of Apias to Karpinos, greetings. We have received from you on account of the artabia-tax 3 1/12 artabai of wheat. (2nd hand) I, Polion, have received as above stated. (1st hand) [Year - - -], Phaophi 15.</ab>
         </div>
